Authenication
-----------------
X509 client certificates
static token file

Authentication ---> Authorization ---> Admission Controllers.
-------
Authorozation Modes..
1. AlwaysDeny - Block all
2. AlwaysAllow - Allow all
3. RBAC - is widely used, uses policies using the K8s API
4. Node - some special permission.

